but I'm about to have a baby, and,
look, I got no husband right now.

1748
01:30:08,440 --> 01:30:11,400
I got no job, and this money
would really, really help me.

1749
01:30:11,490 --> 01:30:13,360
And, you know, let's
be good people and...

1750
01:30:13,450 --> 01:30:16,700
