1765
01:30:49,520 --> 01:30:52,780
It's really not your fault, and
you sound like a very nice person.

1766
01:30:52,860 --> 01:30:55,320
It's just I've been ripped off
one too many times in the past,

1767
01:30:55,400 --> 01:30:57,256
and I'm just not willing to
let that happen to me again.

1768
01:30:57,280 --> 01:31:00,370
So, we're just gonna need to find
a way to get me the money first.

1769
01:31:00,450 --> 01:31:01,870
- You know? Yeah.
<i>- Yeah?</i>

1770
01:31:01,950 --> 01:31:03,700
<i>Listen to me, you
fucking dumb bitch.</i>

1771
01:31:03,790 --> 01:31:05,886
<i>- You're not getting one red cent...</i>
