- I'm sorry.

1838
01:33:38,940 --> 01:33:40,546
Can I have a moment with
her, please? Just to comfort her,

1839
01:33:40,570 --> 01:33:42,070
in privacy with my sister, please?

1840
01:33:42,150 --> 01:33:44,506
- Keep her voice down.
- I'm gonna try, but I gotta calm her down.

1841
01:33:44,530 --> 01:33:46,780
Sorry.

1842
01:33:47,280 --> 01:33:49,790
I don't know what to do.
I don't know what to do.

1843
01:33:51,540 --> 01:33:52,870
That was really good.

1844
01:33:52,960 --> 01:33:54,520
- That was amazing, Rachel.
- Thank you.

1845
01:33:54,580 --> 01:33:55,766
That was so good, it might work.

1846
01:33:55,790 --> 01:33:57,976
